            "DisplayOrder": 410,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 1,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 8000,
            "LocalizeKR": "얼굴은 조금 지저분해졌지만…",
            "LocalizeJP": "顔は少し汚れて\nしまいましたけれども…。",
